      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ :\n\"مَنْ عَالَ اِبْنَتَيْنِ أَوْ أُخْتَيْنِ أَوْ عَمَّتَيْنِ أَوْ خَالَتَيْنِ حَجَبَتَاهُ مِنَ اَلنَّارِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4699 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Whoever takes care of two daughters, two sisters, two paternal aunts, or two maternal aunts, they will shield him from the Fire.\""
        ]
      }
    },
